[color=#aaaacc]Cipher says you're looking for background on a name.

D. Kane. Daniel Marcus Kane.

I know the name. Government-adjacent. Early 2000s. The agency isn't one that gets named in public — you won't find it in a registry. He left, or was made to leave, around 2011. The details aren't something people talk about.

What I can tell you: the people who worked with him don't speak fondly of him. And they don't speak at all, usually.

He knows how to make things disappear. People. Records. Problems.

That's all I've got. Be careful with this one.[/color]

[color=#444466]— vesper[/color]
